{"tid":2366920,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"傳聞指Chris Evans再做「隊長」或參與多於一部Marvel電影 ...","createTime":"2021-01-15T02:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T18:21:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"7a3f0b72a78b0e823c4ef92e675559b65ccf5742","tid":2366920,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:42:46.000Z","msg":"據美國媒體《Deadline》報導，Chris Evans或將回歸MCU，再次飾演「美國隊長」一角。<br />\n<br />\n據《Deadline》報導，Marvel目前正與Chris Evans商討新合約，新合約之下Chris Evans會再次以美國隊長一角，「以某種形式」參與一部Marvel作品，合約亦有可能延伸至另一部電影。消息指「新作品」唔太可能係新一集嘅《Captain America》，但就可能係類似Robert Downey Jr. 於《Iron Man 3》後，出演《Captain America: Civil War》又或者《Spider-Man: Homecoming》嘅配角方式。Marvel暫時未有任何回應。<br />\n<br />\n隊長於《Avengers: Endgame》嘅最後已經成一個老人，亦已經將美國隊長個盾以及身份傳咗畀Anthony Mackie飾演嘅Falcon，Chris Evans本人亦曾多次公開表示自己唔會再做隊長一角&mdash;&mdash;不過2019年尾佢曾經講過，如果有好故事嘅話佢唔排除會再演隊長。消息指近來Marvel方面有意再探索一下Chris Evans嘅隊長仲有冇故事可以講，而Chris Evans本人亦對計劃越黎越有興趣，但暫時亦未有最終決定。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：Deadline<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://deadline.com/2021/01/captain-america-eyes-return-to-the-mcu-as-chris-evans-nears-deal-to-reprise-role-in-future-marvel-project-1234672430/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2021%2F01%2Fcaptain-america-eyes-return-to-the-mcu-as-chris-evans-nears-deal-to-reprise-role-in-future-marvel-project-1234672430%2F&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVT4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=2f562202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://deadline.com/2021/01/captain-america-eyes-return-to-the-mcu-as-chris-evans-nears-deal-to-reprise-role-in-future-marvel-project-1234672430/</a>"},{"pid":"d2d4bc66f044bf53910355153232ad3a10d7685b","tid":2366920,"uid":339805,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:43:28.000Z","msg":"要求由希澈老師取代佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b504ad615335a996eb9be76c4a545fbac2deba88","tid":2366920,"uid":129169,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-